Package: SRP
Title: Stable Random Projection of text into fixed-length vectors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Schmidt", email = "bmschmidt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements a method, "Stable Random Projection", that transform any text into a fixed vector representation suitable for computation. This is provided for convenience; the python version is the canonical one.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports: wordVectors, digest, stringr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
